The wallpaper artwork distributed by this package is a derivative composite:

  - Source line work: Olaus Magnus, Carta Marina (Venice, 1539) — public
    domain; scan from the Bayerische Staatsbibliothek Munich
    (https://www.digitale-sammlungen.de/en/details/bsb00002967).
  - Color reference: 20th-century colored facsimile held by the James Ford
    Bell Library, University of Minnesota, accessed via Google Arts &
    Culture.
  - Compositing, tonal/color adjustment, and final wallpaper crop:
    Hat Labs Ltd, 2026.

The composite is released under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
International License (CC-BY-4.0).

Affected paths:
  - usr/share/halos/wallpapers/halpi.jpg
  - sources/carta-marina-blend.afphoto
  - sources/carta-marina-color-google-arts.jpg

